Using raw binary (Buffer → Blob → URL) is more efficient.

Final Layout Flow
1️⃣ Navbar (with Search Button/Bar)
2️⃣ Hero Section (with #1 trending song & CTA buttons, optional search bar)
3️⃣ Top 10 Ranking Songs Section
4️⃣ Latest 10 Featured Songs Section
5️⃣ Other Sections (Playlists, Recommendations, etc.)
6️⃣ Sticky Footer (Quick Links, Socials, Copyright)

This layout ensures search is easy to access, and the footer provides quick navigation without cluttering the main UI. 🚀🎶

